data.description: Privacy, space and more space is what you will find at this amazing home located in the established Hawthorne community. Featuring three bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms and a loft overlooking the living room... it screams potential. The 1st floor owner's suite is spacious and features a walk-in closet and full bathroom with dual vanities. Out back you have a beautiful oversized deck that does need some serious tlc, and a large private fenced-in backyard. Conveniently located close to shopping, restaurants, & Ft. Liberty. Sellers are selling the property as-is. Don't miss out on this gem, schedule your showing today!
